    <p>Florida OIR tracks complaint data showing premium increases and non-renewal notices as the two most common consumer complaints since 2022. As of Q4 2025, non-renewal complaints remain elevated above pre-Ian levels even as the market shows early signs of stabilization in some inland counties.</p>
