    <p>Several new entrants arrived in Florida from 2023 onward, some backed by reinsurers seeking to take advantage of higher premium rates. Their long-term stability is unproven. When Citizens' depopulation program pushes policies to these newer carriers, the financial strength question is real. Check A.M. Best ratings for any carrier taking over a Citizens policy.</p>
